{"pages": [{"words": {"text": ["Personnel/Insurance", "Committee", "Meeting", "Minutes", "02-21-2017", "Twp.", "Office", "-", "47240", "Green", "Acres", "Road,", "Houghton,", "MI.", "49931", "Where:", "3:00", "PM.", "When", "Convened:", "B.", "Bingham,", "B.", "Petersen", "(Supervisor)", "and", "J.", "Ollila", "Who", "Present:", "Discussion", "Points:", "\uf0b7", "Discussed", "the", "pros", "and", "cons", "for", "the", "Twp.", "of", "offering", "health", "insurance", "buyouts", "for", "our", "full-time", "employees.", "They", "could", "bank", "the", "extra", "income,", "go", "on", "a", "spouse\u2019s", "plan", "or", "enter", "the", "market", "place", "for", "insurance.", "An", "AFLAC", "plan", "was", "also", "discussed", "that", "would", "replace", "lost-time", "wages.", "\u2013", "\uf0b7", "Sick", "leave", "accrual", "was", "discussed", "presently", "the", "staff", "only", "gets", "2", "hours", "per", "pay", "period", "or", "6", "days/year", "sick", "leave.", "Ultimately,", "if", "a", "person", "was", "off", "for", "even", "a", "week", "for", "recuperation", "from", "a", "minor", "surgery", "that", "would", "effectively", "wipe", "out", "his", "sick", "leave", "accrued", "over", "one", "year.", "The", "Comm.", "asked", "the", "Supervisor", "to", "check", "other", "Townships", "to", "see", "what", "they", "are", "doing", "for", "Sick,", "Vacation", "and", "or", "Personnel", "day", "leaves.", "\uf0b7", "A", "DPW", "full-time", "employee", "is", "in", "need", "of", "additional", "bereavement", "days", "because", "his", "\u2013", "sister", "is", "in", "another", "community", "two", "additional", "days", "plus", "the", "three", "presently", "were", "granted.", "Supervisor", "will", "inform", "him", "of", "that.", "\uf0b7", "An", "additional", "DPW", "part-time", "person", "who", "can", "be", "employed", "while", "some", "of", "the", "DPW", "staff", "is", "out", "on", "medical", "leave", "was", "discussed.", "This", "would,", "for", "the", "future", "help", "the", "conti